CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Duration - AR SVC MO]
 AS IIF([Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Duration in Seconds - AR SVC MO]=0 OR ISEMPTY([Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Duration in Seconds - AR SVC MO]),NULL,

[Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Duration in Seconds - AR SVC MO] / 60), 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0.00;-#,##0.00", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Arrangement per Service Month';                               
      
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Megabytes]
 AS IIF([Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Bytes In Bytes]=0 OR ISEMPTY([Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Bytes In Bytes]),NULL,

[Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Bytes In Bytes] / 1024 / 1024), 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0;-#,##0", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Data Service';                              
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Billed At  0 With Indirect Revenue Megabytes - Service]
 AS IIF([Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Bytes in Bytes - Service]=0 OR ISEMPTY([Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Bytes in Bytes - Service]),NULL,

[Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Bytes in Bytes - Service] / 1024 / 1024), 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0;-#,##0", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Master Service Aggregate';                         
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Megabytes - AR SVC MO]
 AS IIF([Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Bytes in Bytes - AR SVC MO]=0 OR ISEMPTY([Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Bytes in Bytes - AR SVC MO]),NULL,

[Measures].[Billed At 0 With Indirect Revenue Bytes in Bytes - AR SVC MO] / 1024 / 1024), 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0;-#,##0", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Arrangement per Service Month';                  
      
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Usage Amount MB - DATA SVC DTL]
 AS [Measures].[Usage Amount in Bytes - DATA SVC DTL], 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0.00;-#,##0.00", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Data Service Detail'; 
CREATE DYNAMIC SET CURRENTCUBE.[Top Ten States - Net Revenue]
 AS TOPCOUNT(
		[Geography Calling].[State Name].Children,
		10,
		[Measures].[Netrevenue]), DISPLAY_FOLDER = 'Sets'  ;                        

SCOPE ([Measures].[Usage Amount MB - DATA SVC DTL]);                       

    SCOPE ([Wallet].[Unit Name].&amp;[Bytes]);                       

        THIS = IIF([Measures].[Usage Amount MB - DATA SVC DTL] =0 OR ISEMPTY([Measures].[Usage Amount MB - DATA SVC DTL]),NULL,
                        [Measures].[Usage Amount MB - DATA SVC DTL] / 1024 / 1024);                       

    END SCOPE;                  
    
END SCOPE;                       

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[New Balance MB - DATA SVC DTL]
 AS [Measures].[New Balance in Bytes - DATA SVC DTL], 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0.00;##0.00", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Data Service Detail';                       

SCOPE ([Measures].[New Balance MB - DATA SVC DTL]);                       

    SCOPE ([Wallet].[Unit Name].&amp;[Bytes]);                       

        THIS = IIF([Measures].[New Balance MB - DATA SVC DTL] =0 OR ISEMPTY([Measures].[New Balance MB - DATA SVC DTL]),NULL,
			[Measures].[New Balance MB - DATA SVC DTL] / 1024 / 1024);                       
         
    END SCOPE;                       

END SCOPE;                    

//Month To Date

    //Fact Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[MTD]);                   

    THIS =
    
        AGGREGATE(
        MTD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember),
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   
    
    END SCOPE;                   

    //Begin Event Date Hierarchy "111"
    SCOPE ([Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[MTD]);                   

    THIS = //  "111";
    
        AGGREGATE(
        MTD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember),
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   

    //End Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[MTD]);                   

    THIS =
    
        AGGREGATE(
        MTD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember),
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                  

//Previous Month To Date

    //Fact Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[MTDPrev]);                 //, [FACT DATE].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =
        
        AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   
    
    END SCOPE;                   

    //Begin Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[MTDPrev]);                 //, [Begin Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =
    
        AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month,
        1,
        [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   

    //End Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[MTDPrev]);                 //, [Begin Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =
    
        AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month,
        1,
        [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                  


//Year To Date

    //Fact Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YTD]);                   

    THIS =
    
        AGGREGATE(
        YTD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember),
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   


    //Begin Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YTD]);                   

    THIS =
    
        AGGREGATE(
        YTD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember),
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   

    //End Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YTD]);                   

    THIS =
    
        AGGREGATE(
        YTD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember),
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                  
 
//Previous Year To Date

    //Fact Date Hierarchy
     SCOPE ([Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YTDPrev]);                 //, [Fact Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =
    
        AGGREGATE(
                YTD(
                    ParallelPeriod([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year,
                    1,
                    [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
                    [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   
       
    END SCOPE;                   


    //Begin Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YTDPrev]);                 //, [Begin Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =
    
        AGGREGATE(
        YTD(
        ParallelPeriod([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year,
        1,
        [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   

    //End Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YTDPrev]);                 //, [End Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =
    
        AGGREGATE(
        YTD(
        ParallelPeriod([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year,
        1,
        [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                  

//Previous Month

    //Fact Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Previous Month]);                 //, [FACT DATE].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

        (PARALLELPERIOD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 1, [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   

    //Begin Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Previous Month]);                 //, [Begin Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

        (PARALLELPERIOD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 1, [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   

    //End Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Previous Month]);                 //, [End Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

        (PARALLELPERIOD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 1, [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   

//Previous Year

    //Fact Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Previous Year]);                 //, [Fact Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

        (PARALLELPERIOD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   

    //Begin Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Previous Year]);                 //, [Begin Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

        (PARALLELPERIOD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   

    //End Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Previous Year]);                 //, [End Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

        (PARALLELPERIOD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   

//Month over Month

    //Fact Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[MoM]);                 //, [Fact Date].[Is Current].&amp;[1]);  
    
    THIS =
           
        (AGGREGATE(
        MTD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember),
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]) 

        -

         AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]));                   

        END SCOPE;                   
    
   // Begin Event Date Hierarchy 
    
        SCOPE ([Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[MoM]);                 //, [Begin Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

       (AGGREGATE(
        	MTD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember),
        	[Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]) 

        -

        AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]));                   

         
    END SCOPE;                 
  
    //End Event Date Hierarchy
        SCOPE ([End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[MoM]);                 //, [End Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

       (AGGREGATE(
        	MTD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember),
        	[End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]) 

        -

        AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]));                   
  
        
    END SCOPE;                   

//Year over Year

    //Fact Date Hierarchy
    
    SCOPE ([Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YoY]);                 //, [FACT DATE].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

        ([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember,  
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])- 

        (PARALLELPERIOD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   
        
    END SCOPE;                   

    //Begin Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YoY]);                 //, [Begin Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

        ([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember,
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])-

        (PARALLELPERIOD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   

    //End Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YoY]);                 //, [End Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

        ([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember,
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])-

        (PARALLELPERIOD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]);                   

    END SCOPE;                   

//Year over Year % Chg

    //Fact Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YoY%]);                  

        SCOPE ([Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YoY%],[Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].[Day].members);                 

             THIS = 
                    // If previous period = 0 then NULL. Else (Current - Previous) / Previous
                    IIF((PARALLELPERIOD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]) = 0, NULL,

                    (([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember,             
                    [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])-

                    (PARALLELPERIOD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]))

                    / (PARALLELPERIOD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]));                  
        END SCOPE;                 

        SCOPE ([Fact Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);                  

            THIS = 
                    IIF((PARALLELPERIOD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]) = 0, NULL,

                    (([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember,             
                    [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])-

                    (PARALLELPERIOD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]))

                    / (PARALLELPERIOD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]));                  
        END SCOPE;                  
    FORMAT_STRING(this) = "Percent";                  
    END SCOPE;                  

    //Begin Event Date Hierarchy
     SCOPE ([Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YoY%]);                  

        SCOPE ([Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YoY%], [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].[Day].members);                   

            THIS =
                    // If previous period = 0 then NULL. Else (Current - Previous) / Previous
                    IIF((PARALLELPERIOD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])  =0, NULL,

                    (([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember,
                    [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])-

                    (PARALLELPERIOD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]))

                    / (PARALLELPERIOD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]));                  
        END SCOPE;                  

        SCOPE ([Begin Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);                 
            
            THIS =
                    // If previous period = 0 then NULL. Else (Current - Previous) / Previous
                    IIF((PARALLELPERIOD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])  =0, NULL,

                    (([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember,
                    [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])-

                    (PARALLELPERIOD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]))

                    / (PARALLELPERIOD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]));                  
        END SCOPE;                  
    FORMAT_STRING(this) = "Percent";                  
    END SCOPE;                   

    //End Event Date Hierarchy
    SCOPE ([End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YoY%]);                 

        SCOPE ([End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[YoY%], [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].[Day].members);                   

            THIS =
                    // If previous period = 0 then NULL. Else (Current - Previous) / Previous
                    IIF((PARALLELPERIOD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])=0, NULL,

                    (([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember,
                    [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])-

                    (PARALLELPERIOD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]))

                    / (PARALLELPERIOD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]));                  
         END SCOPE;                 

         SCOPE ([End Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);                 
    
            THIS =
                    // If previous period = 0 then NULL. Else (Current - Previous) / Previous
                    IIF((PARALLELPERIOD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]) =0, NULL,

                    (([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember,
                    [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])-

                    (PARALLELPERIOD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]))

                    / (PARALLELPERIOD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Year, 1, [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
                    [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]));                 
         END SCOPE;                   
    FORMAT_STRING(this) = "Percent";                  
    END SCOPE;                   


//Month over Month % Chg

    //Fact Date Hierarchy
   
        SCOPE ([Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[MoM%]);                 //, [FACT DATE].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

        // If previous period = 0 then NULL. Else (Current - Previous) / Previous

        IIF(AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])
        
//        (PARALLELPERIOD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 1, [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].currentmember),
//        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])  
        = 0, NULL,

        (AGGREGATE(
        MTD([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember),
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])-

        AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]))

        / 

        AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [Fact Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [Fact Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]));                   
    FORMAT_STRING(this) = "Percent";                  
        END SCOPE;  
               
    
    //Begin Event Date Hierarchy
   
        SCOPE ([Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[MoM%]);                 //, [Begin Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    THIS =

         // If previous period = 0 then NULL. Else (Current - Previous) / Previous
       IIF(AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])
        
        = 0, NULL,

        (AGGREGATE(
        MTD([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember),
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])-

        AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]))

        / 

        AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [Begin Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [Begin Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]));                 
  
    FORMAT_STRING(this) = "Percent";                  
        END SCOPE;                   
   
    //End Event Date Hierarchy
   
        SCOPE ([End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[MoM%]);                 //, [End Event Date].[IS CURRENT].&amp;[1]);  

    
THIS = 
    
        // If previous period = 0 then NULL. Else (Current - Previous) / Previous
        IIF(AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])
        
        = 0, NULL,

        (AGGREGATE(
        MTD([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember),
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals])-

        AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]))

        / 

        AGGREGATE(
        MTD(
        ParallelPeriod([End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].Month, 
        1, 
        [End Event Date].[Date Hierarchy].CurrentMember)),
        [End Event Date Calculations].[Calculation].[Actuals]));                 
  
    FORMAT_STRING(this) = "Percent";                  
        END SCOPE; </Text>
            </Command>
          </Commands>
        </MdxScript>
      </MdxScripts>
    </Cube>
